HEADWORD: Maclurea
<hw>Ma*clu"re*a</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[NL. Named
from <person>William <etsep>Maclure</etsep></person>, the
geologist.]</ety> <fld>(Paleon.)</fld> <def>A genus of spiral gastropod
